actions.label: holding steering wheel
actions.details: A person's gloved hands are holding the steering wheel of a car while driving.

actions.label: manipulating gear stick
actions.details: Left hand moves to and manipulates the gear stick.

actions.label: holding steering wheel
actions.details: Both hands are holding the steering wheel while driving.

actions.label: pulling door handle
actions.details: Right hand moves to and pulls the car door handle.

actions.label: opening car door
actions.details: The car door opens after the handle is pulled.

actions.label: touching steering wheel
actions.details: The person is touching the steering wheel with both hands.

actions.label: manipulating gear stick
actions.details: The person is manipulating the gear stick with their left hand.

actions.label: person looking into engine bay
actions.details: A person is standing next to the car with the hood open, looking into the engine bay.

actions.label: person reaching into engine bay
actions.details: A person reaches their right hand into the car's engine bay.

actions.label: person manipulating component in engine bay
actions.details: A person is manipulating a component within the car's engine bay with their right hand.

actions.label: pointing at car's front
actions.details: The person points their right hand towards the front of the car.

actions.label: moving hand towards car's front
actions.details: The person moves their right hand closer to the car's front bumper.

actions.label: touching car's front bumper
actions.details: The person touches the car's front bumper with their right hand.

actions.label: sliding hand along car's front bumper
actions.details: The person slides their right hand along the car's front bumper, moving from left to right.

actions.label: pointing at car front
actions.details: The person points towards the front of the silver car.

actions.label: touching car front
actions.details: The person touches the front bumper/grille area of the silver car.

actions.label: lifting car hood
actions.details: The person lifts the car hood with both hands.

actions.label: opening car hood
actions.details: The person fully opens the car hood, revealing the engine bay.

actions.label: taking hood prop rod
actions.details: The person takes the hood prop rod from its holder.

actions.label: inserting hood prop rod
actions.details: The person inserts the hood prop rod into the designated hole to keep the hood open.

actions.label: grasping oil dipstick
actions.details: The person grasps the yellow handle of the oil dipstick.

actions.label: pulling out oil dipstick
actions.details: The person pulls the oil dipstick out of the engine.

actions.label: wiping oil dipstick
actions.details: The person uses a blue cloth to wipe the oil from the dipstick.

actions.label: reinserting oil dipstick
actions.details: The person reinserts the clean oil dipstick back into the engine.

actions.label: loosening bolt with wrench
actions.details: The person uses a wrench to loosen a bolt on the car's underside.

actions.label: removing bolt by hand
actions.details: After loosening, the person removes the bolt completely by hand.

actions.label: placing wrench down
actions.details: The person moves the wrench away from the car and places it down.
